Title: 13.1.2 Integer Types (Exact Value) - INTEGER, INT, SMALLINT, TINYINT, MEDIUMINT, BIGINT
Description: A normal-size integer. The signed range is -2147483648 to 2147483647. The unsigned range is 0 to 4294967295.
Type: INT; Storage (Bytes): 4; Minimum Value Signed: -2147483648; Maximum Value Signed: 2147483647; Minimum Value Unsigned: 0; Maximum Value Unsigned: 4294967295
